{"tid":2423923,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴克萊研究指Reddit網民對Tesla股價影響高於基本面及估值","createTime":"2021-02-26T08:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:13:40.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc800b9c678e5e65ad5f32139b97ce267d63fb5","tid":2423923,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:08:48.000Z","msg":"(Tesla Inc.)股價近來大幅拉回，根據巴克萊巴克萊檢視了Reddit知名論壇WallStreetBets (WSB)，發現若提到特斯拉的文章驟增，股價幾天後即會有反應。報告稱，若今日提到「$TSLA」或「TSLA」的相關貼文比昨日多7則以上，即可預測特斯拉明日股價將有超乎標準普爾500指數的報酬，兩者有明顯正相關。(統計圖表見此)<br />\n<br />\n根據巴克萊統計，WSB過去幾日每天僅有2-3則有關特斯拉的貼文，低於過去備受矚目、報酬跳增的趨勢。接下來得觀察，WSB網友的注意力是否會重新轉回TSLA。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.moneydj.com/f1a.aspx?a=0a8e6747-2230-424c-b9fd-47ac1df17a0c&amp;c=MB020000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.moneydj.com%2Ff1a.aspx%3Fa%3D0a8e6747-2230-424c-b9fd-47ac1df17a0c%26c%3DMB020000&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd60B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=1b8e3c35\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.moneydj.com/f1a.aspx?a=0a8e6747-2230-424c-b9fd-47ac1df17a0c&amp;c=MB020000</a>"},{"pid":"d4c10619c6d00d336b3c54494550b0a83bcfb4ba","tid":2423923,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"契媽都係Reddit仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe2fb566c092f281c12d90af28093a807a3c084","tid":2423923,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"下下講基本面有咩用<br />\n港共係咪要跟民意調查施政？"}]}